name: Incacti
description:
W/A/S/D to move 

Leftclick to shoot

Space to stop time (limited use)

fight against some cactus bois collect powerups to get stronger and reach higher rooms the enemys will also get stronger each room. to advance a room kill all the bad cactus bois in one room. this was made for the Low Effort Jam in 1 day 


the rooms are random generated every time and stones can drop powerups if destroyed
